Typed the following into the commit message area and selected "format to guidelines" from the contextual menu:
{quote}
Add basic message bus handling

(Likely this will change to match our existing message handling patterns,
but this outlines it well)
{quote}

Got the following output back:
{quote}
Add basic message bus handling

(Likely this will change to match our existing message handling 
but this outlines it well)
patterns,
{quote}
(Notice that "patterns," has been moved down _two_ lines instead of the expected one.)

But had expected something along the lines of:
{quote}
Add basic message bus handling

(Likely this will change to match our existing message handling 
patterns, but this outlines it well)
{quote}
